                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6210" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1571</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9008 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">紫光集团并购强“芯”之路:是发展半导体还是“绊倒体”?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Tsinghua Unigroup‘s development in semi-conductor: failure or success?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">任成林，谢梦琪，唐晓莹，杨昊天</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">紫光集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">紫光集团；连续并购；芯片半导体；风险</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Tsinghua Unigroup; Continuous acquisition; Semiconductor; Risk</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，中美高新技术领域的竞争、新冠疫情的爆发、5G网络的普及、可穿戴设备以及云服务的发展等因素都深刻地影响了全球半导体行业的发展，对于中国半导体企业来说，既是挑战也是机遇，如何抓住有利的外部机遇，进行快速高质量的发展考验着企业管理层的智慧和选择。本文以国内芯片半导体行业龙头企业紫光集团破产重整事件作为切入点，以其2013年以来长达7年连续并购为背景，解析企业实施连续并购的动因，以及分析企业对并购相关风险的把控。本案例主要用于企业并购战略方面的教学，目的在于让案例使用者深刻理解连续并购的相关理论与实际应用的要点，同时，期望能为半导体行业其他公司战略发展提供一定的参考价值。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, the competition between China and the United States in the field of high-tech, the outbreak of COVID-19, the popularity of 5G network, the development of wearable devices and cloud services and other factors have profoundly affected the development of the global semiconductor industry. For China&#39;s semiconductor industry, it is both a challenge and an opportunity. How to seize favorable external opportunities?  Rapid and high-quality development tests the wisdom and choice of enterprise management.  This paper takes the bankruptcy and reorganization event of Unigroup group, the leading enterprise in the chip and semiconductor industry in China, as the entry point, and takes its continuous m&amp;a for 7 years since 2013 as the background to analyze the motivation for enterprises to implement the continuous M&amp;A and the control of enterprises to the merger-related risks.  This case is mainly used for the teaching of enterprise MERGER and acquisition strategy. The purpose is to let the users of the case deeply understand the key points of the relevant theories and practical application of continuous merger and acquisition. Meanwhile, it is expected to provide some reference value for the strategic development of other companies in the same industry.  </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业并购管理》、《企业风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业连续并购战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-03</td>
                            </tr>
